{"tid":2029594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬可以移民，黑警反而開始移唔到？","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T11:01:57.000Z","uid":216683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dafb0e3e07350c50cbc8ca80b216355cd8400f9","tid":2029594,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"攬炒香港變一國一制<br />\n高壓統治<br />\n<br />\n港豬可以走資移民<br />\n但黑警因為身份問題其他國家移民署唔受理<br />\n因為出哂名係中共隻狗<br />\n唔會收間諜<br />\n<br />\n變相黑警要硬食一國一制<br />\n<br />\n香港人走哂得返班黑警<br />\n中共要清洗香港人，班黑警又要硬食<br />\n<br />\n今次真係condom仔啦<br />\n邊個最唔想有國安法？<br />\n你地覺得呢？<br />\n<br />\n正皮：真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮：黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4679ceb35ad9974f1841af4f4cb87fca691b34","tid":2029594,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"港版國安法：草案內容指國安機關可在港成立機構<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中共有機構係香港執行國安法<br />\n就會騎係黑警上面<br />\n<br />\n呀蛇你覺得自己係香港大哂？<br />\n到時撚你都要含呀<br />\n走？你走得去邊？<br />\n抵撚死<br />\n等入勞改營啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab011a2035bffaa81f4aed45533b6c67f4c199f","tid":2029594,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">524 銅鑼灣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PS6to8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPS6to8O.jpg&h=36a27b19&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}